items.badge_description: Glad you checked in and enjoyed a beer; with 26 taps there’s always something new to try. Plus don’t forget to come to our Craft Beer Fight Club Event, be the first to try the new stuff, details on our website.

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 315 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower.
